55270434, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "我是男生我也不想养育孩子，养不养育孩子应该是自己的选择，女性的身体还是女性做主。\n如果养育孩子会对身体、职业、未来可预见的生活水平都造成负面影响，反感才是正常的吧。", "timestamp": 1655270434}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 218995, "create_time": 1655270441, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "女权主义者不婚是第一要求……怎么还去谈你的一二三条", "timestamp": 1655270441}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 218997, "create_time": 1655270532, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "我不支持的是以养育孩子作为筹码去交换各种利益（房子、彩礼之类），如果不想养那就不养呗。", "timestamp": 1655270532}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 218998, "create_time": 1655270544, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 比如说2，6，9，11，想不想孝敬，喜欢什么样的身材，想不想懂防身技巧，性观念什么样，和你男的有啥关系？", "timestamp": 1655270544}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 219005, "create_time": 1655270645, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 在恶劣的环境下，自然界的生物也会拒绝生育么？ - 知乎\nhttps://www.zhihu.com/question/505954290", "timestamp": 1655270645}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 219055, "create_time": 1655271679, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 为啥非要和男的有关系呢？不能是希望一个更加友好理想的社会上男女关系吗？毕竟双方都要努力变优秀些嘛", "timestamp": 1655271679}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 219064, "create_time": 1655271751, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 谁跟你变优秀，平等就得允许不优秀的人活下去", "timestamp": 1655271751}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 219075, "create_time": 1655271990, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "资本家虽然需要源源不断的劳动力，但不希望打工人把时间花在养孩子上，你不会觉得是女权问题吧？", "timestamp": 1655271990},